title: ShotWatch
description: Developed a full-stack application using AWS Lambda and GraphQL to enable advanced search queries across 615K+ NBA plays, allowing users to filter by shot location, quarter time, and additional play details effortlessly.

title: League of Legends Performance Modeling
description: Implemented a Random Forest classifier model to predict player roles from player performance stats from a dataset of 123,223 games, achieving a 95% F1-score through feature engineering and hyperparameter optimization.

title: Cold Outreach Automation
description: Developed an automated outreach system using nodriver and pandas scraping 100+ Wellfound job listings daily, extracting contacts from Apollo, and automating email outreach, reducing manual effort by 90%.
